      "comment": "BUG ME MORE (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (22.44) from Box 7 at this track. Has won three of six starts from this draw. Rates highly and will give a great sight. BEEP (7) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.02 beating STRAWBERRY WINE. One of the key runners again. HARA'S SUZUKI (2) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at this track and distance (22.11), scoring by 5 lengths. Rates a leading chance again. HOLLYWOOD SHADOW (4) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
